### --- 抢单流程测试 ---

### 4. 注册第二个用户 (充当接单人)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "2021999",
  "password": "123456"
}

### 5. 接单人登录
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "2021999",
  "password": "123456"
}

> {%
    client.global.set("receiver_token", response.body.data.token);
%}

### 6. 抢单 (注意：taskId 必须是刚才发布的那个，去数据库看一眼 id 是多少，假设是 1)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/orders/accept
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{receiver_token}}

{
  "taskId": 1
}

### 7. 确认完成 (注意：必须用发布者的 Token，orderId 去 tb_order 表看)
# 假设生成的 orderId 是 1
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/orders/confirm
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{auth_token}}

{
  "orderId": 1
}

